Z","msg":"我覺得無關係<br />\n就算唔養貓都一樣有其他因素會鼻敏感<br />\n但唔覺得唔養貓會少左發作"},{"pid":"2fb3698525c55f8047792077b57d7f87f4aa8c0c","tid":279341,"uid":23293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T01:19:07.000Z","msg":"我阿媽有鼻敏感,<br />\n搬咗屋先知唔關隻貓事"},{"pid":"ee05b194c5ffa17fb5c45dbc452adc5dd368acbe","tid":279341,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T01:23:05.000Z","msg":"我...好想養，但係敏到會腫"},{"pid":"77c593c0ee7eb167920262b0d2a9b11cc0351fb0","tid":279341,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T01:24:50.000Z","msg":"Check 左致敏源係咩先，有時會係你意想唔到嘅原因<br />\n未必關貓事"},{"pid":"90df7da793308e13d1519b9b2c335b2db2e25eae","tid":279341,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T01:57:01.000Z","msg":"有無人知哮喘有無影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5e7324d814dcafd15a8d06c4d6352daaf0b2bc","tid":279341,"uid":85088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T02:03:39.000Z","msg":"養緊兩隻  由細到大都係鼻敏感 <br />\n養左之後唔覺有乜分別 好似仲好左d"},{"pid":"5923e2eb450f5140ed71b8ee0a58161d72d73bc7","tid":279341,"uid":15753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T02:05:57.000Z","msg":"有養同冇養嗰時一樣<br />\n冇嚴重到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa830a8ab6496fdc20f0c1e8781417ac7be7b42b","tid":279341,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T02:11:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都有鼻敏感，初初對住貓一陣就會流晒眼水，係咁打乞嚏，但對咗好幾年後，竟然無事，好似無咗鼻敏感咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見好多人都係咁，我有個理論<br />\n就係貓毛係會係人既呼吸管道累積<br />\n慢慢形成一層filter，當人習慣左個filter<br />\n就會停止流眼水打乞嚏，有左filter既保護，仲會少左鼻敏感"},{"pid":"b2570cbc24b1ce977a582ef05c340629446e50f6","tid":279341,"uid":66501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T02:23:02.000Z","msg":"有鼻敏感養緊貓<br />\n貓毛唔太關事<br />\n最主要係佢地捐完d多塵地方<br />\n你抱佢就出事<br />\n保持屋企清潔就得"},{"pid":"07254cc7d9e387905ba5053e8692055580923578","tid":279341,"uid":96218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T02:29:02.000Z","msg":"我有鼻敏感 去親寵物店玩狗玩貓都出事 眼腫流鼻水打乞痴 但係前幾日抱住隻ragdoll又冇事喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">題外話真係嗲到不行 公仔咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"efb4d1fd938c644957704490118aaee0206fe256","tid":279341,"uid":25950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T02:38:33.000Z","msg":"鼻敏感未必關貓事<br />\n但要睇你老豆係咪咁諗<br />\n你有愛，再辛苦都可以為咗隻貓忍受<br />\n你老豆未必係咁諗，到時打個吃嚔都賴隻貓，俾說話你聽事少，要你棄養事大<br />\n<br />\n一係同老豆傾清楚<br />\n一係就Sure自己有能力同決心，他朝有一日隻貓俾人趕走，你可以為咗佢搬出去"},{"pid":"9c8a463d287274ac35c6bb1cb7596ad6ebf6796e","tid":279341,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T08:55:46.000Z","msg":"我成家有鼻敏感 養左三隻主人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都同以前冇乜分別 可能致敏源唔係動物<br />\n<br />\nbtw 其實令人鼻敏感唔係動物嘅毛，係動物皮屑先係致敏源"}]}